Hereâ€™s an end-to-end step-by-step guide to set up Grafana + Prometheus + Alertmanager to monitor Kubernetes pod logs, resources, and send alerts â€” with optional Loki integration for log visibility.

ðŸ§° TOOLS USED
Tool	Role
Prometheus	Collects metrics from pods/nodes
Alertmanager	Sends alerts via Email/Slack/etc.
Grafana	Dashboards & Alert visualization
Loki	(Optional) Centralized pod log monitoring
Promtail	(Optional) Sends logs to Loki

